readme: # Laravel Documentation Theme Atom Editor adaptation of Michael Dyrynda's [Laravel Theme for Sublime](https://github.com/michaeldyrynda/Laravel.tmTheme). Pairs well with Atom One Light. ## Why It's hard to find a theme that checks all your boxes, as everyone has different tastes and preferences. I have previously worked using various GitHub-inspired themes, and this one reminds me of those: very clean medium contrast, and not too noisy. ## Screenshots ### PHP ### HTML ### JavaScript/Vue ### CSS/SCSS
